Package org.ireas.mediawiki.exceptions

Contains the exceptions thrown by MediaWiki and the MediaWiki classes.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HttpMediaWikiException
    Thrown if an HTTP error occurs during an API request.
    InvalidResponseException
    Thrown if the data returned by the MediaWiki API does not match the expected format.
    MediaWikiException
    Base class for all checked exceptions thrown in the MediaWiki library and thrown if a general error occurs.
    NoSuchUserException
    Thrown if details for a missing user are queried.

Package org.ireas.mediawiki.exceptions Description

Contains the exceptions thrown by MediaWiki and the MediaWiki classes. All checked exceptions are subclasses of MediaWikiException.
